## 2) MANUSCRIPT TEXT & FIGURES — CC BY‑NC‑ND 4.0

SPDX-License-Identifier: CC-BY-NC-ND-4.0

You are free to **share** (copy and redistribute the material in any medium or format) under the following terms:

- **Attribution (BY)** — You must give appropriate credit.
- **NonCommercial (NC)** — You may not use the material for commercial purposes.
- **NoDerivatives (ND)** — If you remix, transform, or build upon the material, you may not distribute the modified material.

No additional restrictions may be applied. For the full legal code, see:
https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-nd/4.0/legalcode

This section is intended to avoid conflicts with future journal publication while allowing academic sharing.

