## 3) DATA (ORIGINAL) — CC BY 4.0

SPDX-License-Identifier: CC-BY-4.0

You are free to **share** and **adapt** the data for any purpose, even commercially, under the terms of attribution.
Full legal code: https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/legalcode

**Provenance note:** If a CSV was produced by digitizing a published figure owned by others, include a citation and
a note in the README or file header. Only the **derived numeric values** you created are being shared here; the
original figure images are not redistributed.

