## 4) File‑type mapping (suggested)

- `/code`, `/scripts`, `/notebooks` → Section 1 (MIT)
- `/paper`, `/figures` (LaTeX, PDFs, EPS/PNG you authored) → Section 2 (CC BY‑NC‑ND 4.0)
- `/data` (CSV you authored) → Section 3 (CC BY 4.0)
- Third‑party content → keep original license in a subfolder README or file header
